```plantuml
@startuml YW-Ma_Algorithms-Visualizer

actor User
participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
participant "Backend (Node.js)" as Backend
participant "BMap API" as BMap
participant "C++ Executable" as CppExec
participant "Database (MySQL)" as DB

User -> Frontend: Selects algorithm (e.g., Dijkstra)
Frontend -> BMap: Request map data (nodes/edges)
BMap --> Frontend: Return map data
Frontend -> Frontend: Render graph (GraphSVG/GraphTable)

User -> Frontend: Triggers visualization
Frontend -> Backend: POST /execute (algorithm, graph data)
Backend -> CppExec: Execute algorithm (via IPC/file)
CppExec --> Backend: Return algorithm steps
Backend -> DB: Save execution state
DB --> Backend: Confirm save
Backend --> Frontend: Return animation steps

Frontend -> Frontend: Animate steps (GraphSVG)
Frontend -> Frontend: Update table (GraphTable)
Frontend -> Frontend: Display code snippets

User -> Frontend: Requests report
Frontend -> Backend: GET /reports
Backend -> DB: Query execution history
DB --> Backend: Return history
Backend --> Frontend: Return report data
Frontend -> Frontend: Render report (Reports.js)

@enduml
```